{"type": "article", "id": 14961, "title": "U32 – 1", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-16T07:29:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115214freIhTLG8cDFqCkb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款灯来自墨西哥的设计工作室 SHIFT，其棱角分明的外观和金属材质都是现代设计中才能见到的。灯罩的形状源于柏拉图立体，即二十面体，使灯罩有多个不同角度的三角形侧面，看似奇特，却有一种非常特别的平衡感。灯罩外的几根粗线条的钢管与灯保持了距离，黑白色的对比一起强调了这一外形，令人联想起城市里的建筑。<a href=\"http://www.behance.net/gallery/27172495/U32-1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142337O6ZuCUWB18R5b2tA.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142337RNKX5ms2p8l3b4Pa.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"388\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142338DgxwhtBFkZMoC1XP.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"317\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142338mF3iUOYqrB2sHNpg.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"317\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}